Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If that person really is the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to solve the mysteries behind the two locked rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Causing Your eyelids to swell and permeting your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tear drops serve as a prelude to a wealth of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were the real culprit after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything will now be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the mansion of occult manga artist Hirasaka\NReiki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a séance was held during the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And two locked rooms murders were committed back to back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were related to the murder of Hisaraka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Neditor, Sawanami Ichirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, half a month earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dying message of "Kira" was left at the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what is the true meaning behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:45.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,(OPENED LOCKED ROOM)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:45.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE SéANCE'S DOUBLE ROOM MYSTERY CASE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see a Gomera badge I dropped in that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Gomera badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't receive any reports about one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me look for it real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two keys were found inside the drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible to throw the keys into the drawer via that window vent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for them to also put a\Nnotebook atop those and lock the drawer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Notto mention they ripped apart Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nposters and scattered those around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean anything to this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, get out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Justa bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems something is stuck in the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fragment from Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it on top of the flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Investigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the kid from Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see my Karnen Yaiba card inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I dropped it when I came in last night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me look for it real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't foothold in the room that\Ncan reach the window over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, in order to close the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One needs to press the svvitch without letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, on the entrance door...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a padlock on the inside of it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to lock it from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll search for your card if you'd please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the culprit have to go through all\Nthis trouble setting it up as a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s case, it's likely they\Ndid it to make it appear as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there a secret passage or something\Nalong those lines in the meditation room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's like what I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this locked room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will be too tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the locked room mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I lack evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we conduct a search of the meditation\Nroom to see if there's a secret passage of some sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hoonogi Kazuo (28)\NKira Fan / Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Something like that doesn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Not in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your effort will be wasted even if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:58.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Because Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} used magic to escape from the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kani Yutaka (24)\NFan Club Chairman / Figurine Creator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:05.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mifune Ryuuichi (27)\NCameraman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:05.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yatsukawa Kouji (27)\NNichiuri TV Assistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Isn't this room getting a little too warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why don't you loosen your necktie then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,utf come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the police officers are here it'd be bad if I dressed sloppily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Izumi Maho (22)\NKira Fan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No I'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that person just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very likely that the culprit left some conclusive evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, what on earth did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's just over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:34.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just leave the rest to me Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hereby present to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth behind the recent incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:07:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, in this meditation room, we\Nfound Utakura Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was found dead inside his room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next to the body of Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, there\Nwas the rope used to kill Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her cell phone was dropped on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the circumstances, it's natural for us to assume that\NHirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} commited suicide after he killed Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean it wasn't a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, the culprit visited Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And killed him with the poisoned wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They then obtained the padlock key and the room key.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After locking the room from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They killed Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the meditation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next they removed all the decorative\Nposters from their respective panels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And returned to Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They placed the two keys, the rope used as the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cell phone in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to implicate Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuck in the flowers decorated outside Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was a poster fragment we found earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'sthis one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the flowers that was in the vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It follows that the culprit ripped the posters apart in the hallway,\Nand threw the fragments in the room through the window vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would the culprit do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting more and more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I shall demonstrate the trick for the locked room to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were preparing to reconstruct the tricks used in\Nthe locked room under Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, what's that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jumbo-sized Kamen Yaiba movie poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from a friend who's a special effects movie maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you need that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:09:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That poster is the same size as the largest\NKira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} panel available in the room at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit used it in their locked room trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, allow us to begin the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, they rolled up the poster like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing so, they have obtained a thin\Ntube that's about two meters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They then inserted the tube through the window vent\Nand aimed the other end at the opened drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, they simply slipped in the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, they used the tip of the tube to cover the keys with a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After closing the drawer and turning the knob with the tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were able to lock the drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tore apart the posters and threw them in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally sent the emails from\NShouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cell phone to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After throwing the cell phone and the\Nrope back into the room, they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it only requires one poster\Nto accomplish this trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason do they have to carry all of\Nthe posters here and rip them apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did they make this meditation room a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was done by magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} has become a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit did not utilize magic to achieve that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was ninja arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninja arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the culprit was a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I mean is not something preternatural like\Nthe Art of Hidden Explosives or the Art of Cloning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see it on TV often, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninjas would use their katana as a foothold to jump over tali walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit employed a similar technique to escape from this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead of a katana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They made use of those tens of posters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall demonstrate it in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are my subordinates, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the assistance of Detective Chiba's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've prepared matching poster sizes\Nwith the corresponding quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the culprit rolled up ali the posters extracted from the panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They stacked up the same-sized posters before rolling them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing this, they obtained four cylinders with varying lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by taping the four cylinders together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have created a makeshiftfoothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with just using this rolled-up paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could they really climb the window that high?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we roll the paper up into cylindrical shapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their tensile strength can surprisingly\Nsustain the applied vertical pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did they close the window after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the contraption used in the sâance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the pulling force of the fishing line, the\Neasel will hold down the switch in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,All they had to do was return to Hirasaka san's\Nroom and dispose of the posters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And place the remote control back in this room\Namid the confusion follovving the body's discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, who's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit killed not only Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sawanami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} half a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A message indicating the culprit was left at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "Kira", didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sawanami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to point out the culprit's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sawanami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to point out the culprit's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mifune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit, Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, what does that "Kira"\Nmessage left at the scene mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sawanami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanted to write "Mifune" in katakana...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But drew his last breath upon finishing "Mifu".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The primary discoverer, Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, saw that\Nand hurriedly added a vertical stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making it say "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason d id she have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was trying to protect you, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is all just speculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any solid proof to back it up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it on your personage, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, despite the fact that you usually like to loosen your tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chose to bear with the heat and wear your tie properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof is hidden underneath that necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time you poisoned Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wine splashed up as the glass was knocked over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And landed on your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would be inconvenienced if the police\Nsearched your personal items during questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's whyi ou ikept the shirt on andihid it with your tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we have that smudge traced, we should conclude a\Nmatch to Hirasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wine at the time of his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who killed those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because they murdered Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kira I loved more than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you really were dating Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, although I had to conceal the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really painful for me to rip apart\NKira's posters with my bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I believe I can save Kira by doing this, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was impossible for Kira, who strictly abided\Nby safe driving, to have had an accident on that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police never gave a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something must've gone on at the party\Nin this mansion before her accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to ascertain the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I planted a number of listening devices all over the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough of your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, Hirasaka had given himself\Nover to alcohol because of his deep slump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirasaka was severely drunk and got into a frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kira tried to calm him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hirasaka forcefully shoved her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to conceal the truth, Hirasaka and\Nthe others disguised it as an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you sought revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I assaulted Sawanami first\Nis because his guard was the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The things you've done, Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sawanami did mention that there was also a girl at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't tell me her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guickly realized it was Shouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just trying to cover up for his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I actually wanted to kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using your gadgets at the séance since I already\Nknew about them from the listening bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive that woman who tried to threaten\Nme despite her involvement with Kira's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to kill that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl at the party with Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} that day was actually me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, why didn't Sawanami mention your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's because Sawanami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It felt like he wasn't interested in a boring woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought she was the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you report to the police immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't want to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} was really gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} was my only hope to live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being bullied through middle and high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd secluded myself from people, even as an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was thanks to Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} that I could live a normal life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to meet Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} on the fateful day I decided\Nto muster the courage to visit a-cosplay shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most people might see cosplay as just a pastime, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To immers'e in the character's imaginative\Nworld even if it's just for a short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was able to forget the painful reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} who taught me that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wished everything that happened was all just a bad dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I reported it to the police and made everything clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would be forced to take in the cruel reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was what I was scared of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only she hadn't done things like threaten Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was not true either...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was in love with Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Shouko dating Sawanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she thought Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was enthralled by Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had to bury her feelings deep down in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she really wanted to help you, Mifune san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She honestly wanted to cover it up for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet I killed her with my own hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason there wasn't any defensive\Nmarks on Shouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was probably because she lost hope and gave\Nup struggling when you attacked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lies, lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, a lie, a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'sa lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did he have to make this place a sealed room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is only my speculation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wanted the police to tear down\Nthis room by making it appear to be sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants us to tear it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we couldn't solve the locked room mystery, we'd\Nlook into the possibility of a secret passage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we'd do as much as tearing up the floorboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing so he wanted the police to discover...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body that was hidden under\Nthe flooring by Hirasaka and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the police did write off Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death as an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next day, during the police investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They unearthed Kira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body\NUnderneath the meditation room flooring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that, ali the locked rooms have been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yatsukawa, I heard you won the Director's\NAward because of your reporting the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But many of my acquaintances have been killed or arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please assist me with my next assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thistime, I'll be doing a report on a haunted hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filled with supernatural phenomena!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let'sgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's set foot right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, don't grab me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had enough of the occult stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, we've had enough.
